text:
Spicy food lover approved!! Kene try.
Lauk berado fav!
Affordable price for breakfast and lunch. Lauk banyak ‘kampung vibe’ kinda style.
Great kampung style food. Friendly staff.

I must admit that this place offers good food and a good environment. But the owner should consider to top-up their side dish as I came in during lunch hour and the food is almost finished. If he keeping this up then I suggest just take the business to the road side as people waste their time to drive but only to find out that the food is finished
One of my favorite lunch spots. Affordable & delicious mixed rice. Other foods such as meatballs, bakwan, chicken penyek are delicious. Favorite is meatballs, the meat doesn't come off straight away.
Delicious food, fast order service, friendly again, I recommend this shop, addicted to eating there,
